Name: add photo

Description: The user will be able to add a profile picture

Players: user, admin, DB

Preconditions: The user have to be already registered and login, and a picture on the phone that he would like to put as a profile picture

Basic flow:
	1) login
	2) Menu shows up
	3) click on add photo
	4) adding photo page shows up
  5) click on choose from gallery
  6) the photo gallery from the user's phone shows up
  7) click on photo
  8) click on choose

Alternate flow:---------------

Exception flow: If the user has no pictures on the phone, his gallery will be empty and he will not be able to select a profile picture


Post conditions: the user have a profile picture
